# ecosystem-index

Display the AIOS Ecosystem Index with all minds and agents.

## Usage

```bash
/ecosystem-index          # Show complete index
/ecosystem-index minds    # Show only minds section
/ecosystem-index agents   # Show only agents section
/ecosystem-index squads   # Show only squads section
```

## Subcommands

- **`/ecosystem-index`** - Displays the complete ecosystem index
- **`/ecosystem-index minds`** - Filters to show only the Minds section
- **`/ecosystem-index agents`** - Filters to show only Core Agents section
- **`/ecosystem-index squads`** - Filters to show only Squad Agents section

## How It Works

Reads `docs/ECOSYSTEM-INDEX.md` and displays the requested section(s).

## Regenerate Index

If the index is outdated, regenerate it with:

```bash
node scripts/generate-ecosystem-index.js
```

---

**Implementation:**

Read `docs/ECOSYSTEM-INDEX.md` and filter sections based on the subcommand argument.
